This power... no doubt about it, she's a \c[2]Guardians\c[0]
magical girl!

To think she would jump right into our lap... this saves us
the trouble.

Attention all combatants, a \c[2]Guardians\c[0] magical girl
has infiltrated the facility.

Commence capture operations immediately! If necessary, you
are authorized to use the \c[2]Spirit Power Absorption\c[0]
equipment!

When those with Spirit Power are \c[2]mentally
cornered\c[0], their barriers weaken, making absorption
possible...

And it has been proven through experiments that these
barriers are at their weakest when receiving \c[2]sexual
pleasure\c[0].

Now, let's take our time and see just how much Spirit Power
we can get from this magical girl!

Kohane-chan's hunches are usually right, so we better stay
sharp and keep moving.
It seems there are no traps in this area.
